aso Barea, Vito Lombardi"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/ee089b9ddb8981ed7e532c32e5205bd5" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Raffaella-Petrosino-150x142.jpg" width="100" height="95" alt="Raffaella Petrosino" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Raffaella Petrosino"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/raffaella-petrosino/">View all articles by Raffaella Petrosino</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2016/03/sacre-di-sasha-waltz-al-teatro-real-di-madrid/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> “Sacre” di Sasha Waltz al Teatro Real di Madrid</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2016/03/milano-teatro-alla-scala-lo-schiaccianoci-2/" rel="next">Milano, Teatro alla Scala: &#8220;Lo Schiaccianoci&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" name="s" id="s" placeholder="Search" /> <button type="submit" class="submit btn" name="submit" id="searchsubmit"><i class="icon-search"></i></button></form> </aside><aside id="ct-relatedposts-widget-2" class="widget ct-relatedposts-widget clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">Articoli correlati</h3><ul class="related-posts-single clearfix"><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/martina-franca-42-festival-della-valle-ditria-la-grotta-di-trofonio/' title='Martina Franca, 42° Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="la grotta di Trofonio, Martina Franca 2016" title="Martina Franca, 42° Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/opera-di-firenze-cortile-di-palazzo-pitti-la-traviata/' title='Opera di Firenze, Cortile di Palazzo Pitti: &#8220;La Traviata&#8221;'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="La traviata (prima) Simone Donati - TerraProject - Contrasto (10)" title="Opera di Firenze, Cortile di Palazzo Pitti: &#8220;La Traviata&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-prima-Simone-Donati-TerraProject-Contrasto-10-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/La-traviata-pr